11:
Allow me, my lord.
O Spirits, bestow unto us Light's
providence!
20:
I'm going all out!
Full power!
34:
Eek! I thought I said no hugging,
Pecorine!
39:
We've defeated the golem, but...
nothing seems to have changed.
43:
Huh? What was supposed to
change?
47:
I figured that maybe this is all a
vision, shown to us by the ruins we're
exploring.
50:
Except it's NOT a dream. That meat
we had before couldn't have been
more real.
54:
Then there is no doubt. We have
truly been transported to a foreign
land.
59:
But there's no such place as
Palpebra! I've never heard of it
before!
68:
Allow us to explain the matter
further while we make our way back
to the Guild.
75:
You mean we've been teleported to
an entirely DIFFERENT WORLD?!
78:
Yes... You see, you came out of a
place called the Kaleidoscope.
80:
It's not uncommon for people from
totally different worlds to end up
there.
85:
I see. Then we are stranded here, is
that correct?
90:
Stranded?! W-w-what are we
supposed to do? Can we get home?!
106:
Don't you worry! You see, the
Adventurer's Guild is perfectly
equipped to help guide newcomers
to this world!
110:
We'll help you get adjusted to your
new life in Palpebra pronto! We've
got rooms prepared, and we'll be
able to hook you up with work as
well!
114:
Food please!
I'd like food first!
118:
O-oh, okay! I'll lend you some
money for the time being, but
please be... deliberate and careful in
how you use it!
122: What do you make of this, my lord?
127:
Ngh... Guess you're right. We'll need
a base of operations while we try to
find a way to get back to Landosol.
131:
In that case, we will gladly accept
your offer, Lady Pur Lilie.
136:
Excellent! Leave the formalities to
me! First, I'll find suitable
accommodations for you all!
140:
My lord and I shall be in the same
quarters, so we won't need more
than three rooms.
145:
Koro! How many times do I have to
tell you to stop being so
overprotective?
150:
Hehe. This reminds me of when we
first started the Gourmet Guild.
156:
Perhaps this can be the Palpebra
Branch of the Gourmet Guild, then.
161:
Yes! Ooh, I can't wait to see what
kind of foods they have here on this
world!
167:
This isn't a vacation! We don't have
time for food tours!
170:
It's great to see such a close group
of friends. They're very lively.
174:
No kidding! I think they'll be able to
take care of themselves just fine.
178:
No, we should be the ones thanking
you! You were a big help cleaning
up that golem.
181:
If you are ever in need of assistance,
do not hesitate to ask.
184:
If you're staying in Palpebra, I'm sure
we'll have plenty of opportunity to
talk later on!
